# Ephemeral runtime state — do not commit
STATUS.md

# Everything else IS committed:
#   .autopilot/config.md     — the session's idea, criteria, thresholds
#   .autopilot/iteration-N/  — per-iteration artifacts (ideas, discussion, evaluation, summary)
#   .autopilot/HISTORY.md    — consolidated cross-iteration log (durable, resume-critical)
#   .autopilot/FINAL.md      — final report when loop terminates
#   .autopilot/archive/      — snapshots of prior sessions (written when user chooses "Start fresh")
